RCW
82.08.0203
Exemptions
—
Trail grooming services.
The tax levied by RCW
82.08.020
does not apply to sales of trail grooming services to the state of Washington or nonprofit corporations organized under chapter
24.03A
RCW. For the purposes of this section, &quot;trail grooming&quot; means the activity of snow compacting, snow redistribution, or snow removal on state-owned or privately owned trails.
[
2021 c 176 s 5248
;
2008 c 260 s 1
.]
